text: Young Oak Kim (; born October 18, 1962) is a South Korean-born American Republican politician. She is a member of the United States House of Representatives from California's 39th congressional district since 2021. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from California Category:South Korean politicians Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Naturalized citizens of the United States
